{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt","slug":"squirrels-acorn-hunt","title":"Squirrel's Acorn Hunt","title_ko":"다람쥐의 도토리 찾기","level":"A1","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/cover.webp","summary_ko":"겨울을 앞두고 다람쥐가 도토리를 숨기고, 잊힌 도토리가 봄에 새 나무로 자라요.","wordCount":110,"pages":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Winter is coming soon.","translation_ko":"곧 겨울이 와요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Winter","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":440},{"word":"is","charStart":7,"charEnd":9,"startMs":440,"endMs":720},{"word":"coming","charStart":10,"charEnd":16,"startMs":720,"endMs":1060},{"word":"soon","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1460}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"A little squirrel runs to the big oak tree.","translation_ko":"작은 다람쥐가 커다란 참나무로 달려가요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"little","charStart":2,"charEnd":8,"startMs":220,"endMs":540},{"word":"squirrel","charStart":9,"charEnd":17,"startMs":540,"endMs":880},{"word":"runs","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":880,"endMs":1480},{"word":"to","charStart":23,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1700},{"word":"the","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1700,"endMs":1880},{"word":"big","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2240},{"word":"oak","charStart":34,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2240,"endMs":2460},{"word":"tree","charStart":38,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2460,"endMs":2720}]}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"She looks down and finds one acorn.","translation_ko":"다람쥐가 아래를 보니 도토리 하나가 있어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":820},{"word":"looks","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":820,"endMs":1020},{"word":"down","charStart":10,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1380},{"word":"and","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1680},{"word":"finds","charStart":19,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1680,"endMs":1900},{"word":"one","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2300},{"word":"acorn","charStart":29,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2600}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"One acorn!\" she says.","translation_ko":"\"도토리 한 개!\" 다람쥐가 말해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":760},{"word":"acorn","charStart":5,"charEnd":10,"startMs":760,"endMs":1220},{"word":"she","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2020},{"word":"says","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2340}]}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"Then she finds two more acorns.","translation_ko":"그러고는 도토리 두 개를 더 찾아요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Then","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"she","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":300,"endMs":500},{"word":"finds","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":500,"endMs":780},{"word":"two","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":780,"endMs":1100},{"word":"more","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1360},{"word":"acorns","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1720}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"One, two, three acorns are in her paws.","translation_ko":"하나, 둘, 셋, 도토리가 다람쥐 손에 있어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"two","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":760,"endMs":1060},{"word":"three","charStart":10,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1720},{"word":"acorns","charStart":16,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1720,"endMs":2040},{"word":"are","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2360},{"word":"in","charStart":27,"charEnd":29,"startMs":2360,"endMs":2480},{"word":"her","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2480,"endMs":2640},{"word":"paws","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2640,"endMs":3000}]}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"She runs and runs under the tall trees.","translation_ko":"다람쥐는 높은 나무들 아래로 달리고 또 달려요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"runs","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":300,"endMs":680},{"word":"and","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":680,"endMs":1020},{"word":"runs","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1300},{"word":"under","charStart":18,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1600},{"word":"the","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1820},{"word":"tall","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2100},{"word":"trees","charStart":33,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2500}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"Soon she has many acorns.","translation_ko":"곧 다람쥐에게 도토리가 아주 많아져요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Soon","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":520},{"word":"she","charStart":5,"charEnd":8,"startMs":660,"endMs":940},{"word":"has","charStart":9,"charEnd":12,"startMs":940,"endMs":1260},{"word":"many","charStart":13,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1700},{"word":"acorns","charStart":18,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1700,"endMs":2120}]}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"She hides the acorns in the soft ground.","translation_ko":"다람쥐는 부드러운 땅속에 도토리를 숨겨요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"She","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"hides","charStart":4,"charEnd":9,"startMs":300,"endMs":640},{"word":"the","charStart":10,"charEnd":13,"startMs":640,"endMs":960},{"word":"acorns","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":960,"endMs":1300},{"word":"in","charStart":21,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1300,"endMs":1500},{"word":"the","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1760},{"word":"soft","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1760,"endMs":1940},{"word":"ground","charStart":33,"charEnd":39,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2320}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Now I have food for winter,\" she says.","translation_ko":"\"이제 겨울에 먹을 게 있어요.\" 다람쥐가 말해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Now","charStart":1,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"I","charStart":5,"charEnd":6,"startMs":360,"endMs":620},{"word":"have","charStart":7,"charEnd":11,"startMs":620,"endMs":860},{"word":"food","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":860,"endMs":1200},{"word":"for","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1520},{"word":"winter","charStart":21,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1520,"endMs":2160},{"word":"she","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2320},{"word":"says","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2620}]}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"But she forgets one little acorn.","translation_ko":"하지만 작은 도토리 하나를 깜빡 잊어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"she","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":220,"endMs":480},{"word":"forgets","charStart":8,"charEnd":15,"startMs":480,"endMs":1280},{"word":"one","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1640},{"word":"little","charStart":20,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1640,"endMs":1880},{"word":"acorn","charStart":27,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2120}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"It sleeps under the cold snow.","translation_ko":"그 도토리는 차가운 눈 아래에서 잠을 자요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"It","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"sleeps","charStart":3,"charEnd":9,"startMs":300,"endMs":560},{"word":"under","charStart":10,"charEnd":15,"startMs":560,"endMs":840},{"word":"the","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":840,"endMs":1200},{"word":"cold","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1340},{"word":"snow","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1640}]}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"Spring comes, and the snow melts away.","translation_ko":"봄이 오고, 눈이 사르르 녹아요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Spring","charStart":0,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"comes","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":420,"endMs":880},{"word":"and","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1240,"endMs":1280},{"word":"the","charStart":18,"charEnd":21,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1500},{"word":"snow","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1500,"endMs":1700},{"word":"melts","charStart":27,"charEnd":32,"startMs":1700,"endMs":2020},{"word":"away","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2320}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"A tiny green plant grows up from the acorn.","translation_ko":"도토리에서 작고 푸른 새싹이 쑥 자라나요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"A","charStart":0,"charEnd":1,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"tiny","charStart":2,"charEnd":6,"startMs":220,"endMs":680},{"word":"green","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":680,"endMs":1060},{"word":"plant","charStart":13,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1060,"endMs":1440},{"word":"grows","charStart":19,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1820},{"word":"up","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1820,"endMs":2080},{"word":"from","charStart":28,"charEnd":32,"startMs":2080,"endMs":2260},{"word":"the","charStart":33,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2260,"endMs":2420},{"word":"acorn","charStart":37,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2720}]}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"The little plant becomes a new oak tree.","translation_ko":"작은 새싹은 새 참나무가 돼요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":220},{"word":"little","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":220,"endMs":440},{"word":"plant","charStart":11,"charEnd":16,"startMs":440,"endMs":740},{"word":"becomes","charStart":17,"charEnd":24,"startMs":740,"endMs":1200},{"word":"a","charStart":25,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1440},{"word":"new","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1440,"endMs":1620},{"word":"oak","charStart":31,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1860},{"word":"tree","charStart":35,"charEnd":39,"startMs":1860,"endMs":2080}]},{"id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"The lost acorn is a happy gift.","translation_ko":"잊힌 도토리는 기쁜 선물이에요.","audioUrl":"/seed/squirrels-acorn-hunt/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"The","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"lost","charStart":4,"charEnd":8,"startMs":260,"endMs":620},{"word":"acorn","charStart":9,"charEnd":14,"startMs":620,"endMs":1140},{"word":"is","charStart":15,"charEnd":17,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1560},{"word":"a","charStart":18,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1880},{"word":"happy","charStart":20,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2060},{"word":"gift","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2400}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"다람쥐가 도토리를 처음 찾은 곳은 어디인가요?","type":"mc","options":["집 안","강가","바위 위","큰 참나무 아래"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"다람쥐는 커다란 참나무로 달려가 그 아래에서 도토리를 찾았어요.","id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"다람쥐는 도토리를 어디에 숨겼나요?","type":"mc","options":["나뭇가지 위","바위 틈","물속","부드러운 땅속"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"다람쥐는 부드러운 땅속에 도토리를 숨겼어요.","id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"다람쥐가 도토리를 모은 까닭은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["팔려고","장난감으로 쓰려고","겨울에 먹으려고","친구에게 주려고"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"곧 겨울이 와서 먹을거리가 필요했기 때문이에요.","id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"잊어버린 도토리에게 무슨 일이 생겼나요?","type":"mc","options":["새가 먹었어요","강에 떠내려갔어요","새 나무로 자랐어요","녹아 사라졌어요"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"땅속에 남은 도토리는 봄에 싹이 터서 새 참나무가 되었어요.","id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 주는 따뜻한 느낌은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["도토리는 맛이 없어요","겨울은 무서워요","혼자 노는 게 좋아요","작은 실수도 좋은 선물이 될 수 있어요"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"깜빡 잊은 도토리 하나가 새 나무가 되어, 작은 실수도 기쁜 선물이 될 수 있음을 보여줘요.","id":"squirrels-acorn-hunt-q5","ord":4}]}